## Preliminary Findings
- **Common Pattern Interrupts**: Large, high-contrast text on black backgrounds (top/bottom bars). Split screens (3-tier layout). Unexpected combinations (e.g., "Elementary student" + "GPT Trading").
- **Audio Strategy**: (Inferred) High-energy beat, rhythmic SFX (whoosh/pop) synchronized with text appearance.
- **Subtitle Style**: Large, bold fonts (Noto Sans KR or similar), color-coded keywords (Yellow, Green, Red).
- **Narrative Hook**: "Fear/Mistake" hooks (Don't do X), "Payoff/Result" hooks (Outcome of X), "Status/Social Proof" hooks (Yonsei student, 140k subs).

